			depends on BR2_LV_USE_FONT_SUBPX
			depends on BR2_PACKAGE_LVGL_VERSION_8
			help
				Set the pixel order of the display.
				Important only if "subpx fonts" are used.
				With "normal" font it doesn't matter.

